This paper discusses the development of AI models for healthcare systems, which falls under the category of computational biology and bioinformatics (cs.CY). The paper also focuses on the development process of deep learning models, which is a common topic in machine learning (cs.LG) and computer vision (cs.CV) research. Additionally, the paper discusses the importance of engaging stakeholders and educating them about the development process, which is relevant to the field of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
